        <abstract> 
<p>Is studying <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Raises two questions for CD: on the great percentage of female illegitimate births compared with legitimate,</p>
            <p>and on clothing as accounting for hairlessness of humans.</p>
        </abstract>
